    {
      "start_time": 112,
      "end_time": 130,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "[Off mic]. Thanks for everybody to come out. I've really enjoyed this show so far. Can we get a little bit lower lights here on my face. [Unintelligible]. Thanks, yeah, that's good. Uh. Yeah. Okay."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "category": "Performers and Speakers",
          "tag": "Karl Jirgens"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "1309de24-29e7-4f72-8405-5d6f92990c3b"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 130,
      "end_time": 176,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "[On mic]. He said talk in the mic. [Laughs]. Um. Yeah, I'd like to thank Alan Lord and especially Joe. Everybody. Um. I'd like to begin tonight by talking about the pieces that I won't be doing. Uh. That's because there were a lot of well-intentioned people who wanted to make it out here tonight but they couldn't make it so I'm dedicating this to them. Can we have the lights here in the centre, is that possible? Okay. Don't worry about it. Actually, uh, I was gonna do a poem called \"Le Moncole de Mon Oncle\", but uh, I think that's been done by somebody. Uh, I was gonna do a zen piece called \"My Karma Ran Over Your Dogma\"."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "category": "Performers and Speakers",
          "tag": "Karl Jirgens"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "4c147ca4-dcf1-4a35-9fe3-5d3bfc23ca3b"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 176,
      "end_time": 178,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Chatter and laughter."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "category": "Setting and Tech",
          "tag": "Audience"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "cfd347db-9b7d-4fdd-b3f4-eb9eb40ec5c9"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 178,
      "end_time": 216,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "And maybe a, maybe a rap piece 'cause I hear rap is popular though I haven't heard any in Montreal yet. It's called uh, it's got a long title: \"He Was a Winnebago Dego Living Down in Tobego Eatin' a Tomato, Big Fat Tomato, it Was a Deglo Winnebego in the Bushes of Tobego\". Like, the title's almost as long as the piece but [coughs]. Then I was gonna do a, I heard Sylvere's here so I thought maybe what would be appropriate would be a social realist piece, you know so I have one called \"He Got a Temporary Permanent Job at Permanent Trust But He Really Wanted a Permanent Temporary Job at the Dairy Queen\"."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "category": "Performers and Speakers",
          "tag": "Karl Jirgens"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "4d9d6523-b72f-4b93-ba67-0b59f0e1550d"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 216,
      "end_time": 221,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Laughter."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "category": "Setting and Tech",
          "tag": "Audience"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "3a75d86a-4ef3-4fc5-9b2b-2d70f64bcde5"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 221,
      "end_time": 238,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "And uh, I was gonna do a piece called \"Address to America\". It's actually a triple pun, it's 'address' as in US mail or 'a dress' as in US female or 'address' as in I'm talking to you."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "category": "Performers and Speakers",
          "tag": "Karl Jirgens"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "ed86c858-3628-4224-9887-ace5e114af63"
    },
    {
      "start_time": 238,
      "end_time": 272,
      "annotation": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "children": [
            {
              "text": "Starts reciting \"Address to America\" [English]."
            }
          ]
        }
      ],
      "tags": [
        {
          "category": "Performers and Speakers",
          "tag": "Karl Jirgens"
        }
      ],
      "uuid": "42b61253-c400-4bb9-806a-0a65690b228b"
    },
    {
